To build the code run 'make' from inside this directory.
You should have these commands already ran: 

sudo apt-get install cmake
sudo apt-get install freeglut3-dev
sudo apt-get install mesa-common-dev
sudo apt-get install xorg-dev libglu1-mesa-dev
sudo apt-get install libpthread-stubs0-dev

To install aduio packages if needed in SoundAll.h, use this command
sudo apt-get install libsfml-dev lsfml-audio

To run, after compiling the code, run './a.out' from within the terminal in the current directory.

The master file containing all the code is : 16.cpp

Also, the project is being maintained at the link: https://github.com/abhiagar90/dejavu/.
